Fire Profiler Module for Kohana PHP Framework
----------------------------------------------
http://github.com/justinhernandez/fire_profiler/tree/master

Fire Profiler in module form. Shortened class name to FP and made class methods
static. By default FirePHP output is suppressed in production mode. Thanks dlib.


Examples:
-----------
FP::benchmarks(); <-- Kohana benchmarks
FP::database();   <-- Database queries
FP::session();    <-- Session data
FP::post();       <-- Post data
FP::get();        <-- Get data
FP::cookies();    <-- Cookie data
FP::env();        <-- All of the above methods

Other methods:
-----------------
FP::disable(); <-- Disable output for specific page
FP::log($data, 'my_label');
FP::info('hello', 'my_info_label');
FP::warn($watch_out, 'warning');
FP::error($error_message, 'yikes');


FirePHP Class Version: 0.3

Install Firebug:
	https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/1843

Install FirePHP:
	https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/6149

Original Source:
	http://learn.kohanaphp.com/2008/07/21/introducing-fire-profiler/
